  "notes": [
    "Solscan is a read-only explorer; it never blocks or executes anything. The token details page has a dedicated Extensions tab.",
    "It relies on the standard jsonParsed RPC encoding (solana account-decoder), which decodes all stable Token-2022 extensions.",
    "Confidential transfer extensions are partial: config/authorities are shown but ElGamal-encrypted balances and amounts are ciphertext no read-only viewer can render as plaintext."
